{"tid":2486164,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"［何文田/旺角] 點睇太平道/勝利道/何文田街一帶？","createTime":"2021-04-12T16:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T14:32:04.000Z","uid":56758,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bee6b5e8d06c6289b9607f82189b83d699cb9680","tid":2486164,"uid":56758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T16:36:34.000Z","msg":"嗰頭都幾多餐廳<br />\n又算靜<br />\n行十分鐘左右就到旺角<br />\n搭兩三個站巴士就到油麻地地鐵站<br />\n之前睇過太平道幾個盤300呎鬆d都好似唔錯<br />\n不過多數都接近30年樓齡了同埋怕火車橋隔離會好嘈<br />\n何文田街加埋落去純粹因為之前單春套劇拍到好好feel<br />\n我知價錢有段距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無住附近嘅巴打分享下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248ae38b3cd5cf6f6d0818e0e0af3a76c034b8ac","tid":2486164,"uid":199670,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T16:47:11.000Z","msg":"旺角太嘈住到你想死 樓下又多人又雜"},{"pid":"b8850c2f8734e8fc4568452ab37f269ef0dd0136","tid":2486164,"uid":72630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T23:05:22.000Z","msg":"何文田街幾好，係樓舊少少同埋無乜靚盤<br />\n<br />\n但旁邊有新樓就快落成（祐滿街），想要新樓可以考慮"},{"pid":"34282a0e05f87ac173a0cec7799d6c199543a78d","tid":2486164,"uid":72630,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T23:07:13.000Z","msg":"勝利道太平道就唔推薦。勝利道有地盤，家陣係嘈加空氣差，食野既話，你係何文田街行去都係多兩三分鐘，但環境贏一大段"},{"pid":"bfb6084f664008ada3fe78e46a788bb9c15f53b5","tid":2486164,"uid":13316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"248ae38b3cd5cf6f6d0818e0e0af3a76c034b8ac","tid":2486164,"uid":199670,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T16:47:11.000Z","msg":"旺角太嘈住到你想死 樓下又多人又雜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T23:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf0857ca8fdbdf28ad87fada753100b4e5e0bd2","tid":2486164,"uid":96854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:38:40.000Z","msg":"住過富威，我認為好好住！我果時住個位數樓層，最concern係有冇火車聲。但實測唔係幾聽到，只有深夜好靜時先微微聽到。<br />\n果頭同旺角隔左條街個feel完全唔同，好有小社區感覺，但過少少就旺角，行街食飯買嘢都方便，仲要去邊都一程車，堅係靜中帶旺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 梭椏道間flat iron好食得嚟幾抵食"},{"pid":"da205c75dbfd841dbdbbacfc848cb3b964797ab1","tid":2486164,"uid":8812,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:41:36.000Z","msg":"交通垃圾，得D ON9小巴會輕，D車又疏，無車真係唔洗諗"},{"pid":"3728caed8027c338ab6c15950b585359043e4055","tid":2486164,"uid":56546,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"da205c75dbfd841dbdbbacfc848cb3b964797ab1","tid":2486164,"uid":8812,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:41:36.000Z","msg":"交通垃圾，得D ON9小巴會輕，D車又疏，無車真係唔洗諗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:44:02.000Z","msg":"行5分鐘去到旺角啦喎<br />\n<br />\n想坐咩車都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf46f6736e2014e6599247f3b33b784ae974ee5","tid":2486164,"uid":72630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3728caed8027c338ab6c15950b585359043e4055","tid":2486164,"uid":56546,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"da205c75dbfd841dbdbbacfc848cb3b964797ab1","tid":2486164,"uid":8812,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:41:36.000Z","msg":"交通垃圾，得D ON9小巴會輕，D車又疏，無車真係唔洗諗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:44:02.000Z","msg":"行5分鐘去到旺角啦喎<br />\n<br />\n想坐咩車都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T04:32:20.000Z","msg":"仲有大把巴士喎"},{"pid":"9de52e77e4a90bb1e6b9104bfd0f1ca80a2015ae","tid":2486164,"uid":10202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T08:42:21.000Z","msg":"火車橋唔洗擔心，一d都唔嘈"},{"pid":"a3214ca856c56bf91ce745e0831c8d088bfa71a5","tid":2486164,"uid":64449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:25:35.000Z","msg":"一步上加多利山吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927eb11741521f7c384178b939737f62599bfee0","tid":2486164,"uid":42690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:49:27.000Z","msg":"住緊太平道 唔算嘈 都幾靜<br />\n食嘢樓下附近最近多咗好多餐廳 食到厭行出旺角食都好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搭車方面 行去旺角站就5分鐘左右 巴士就行出亞皆老街/窩打老道都大把<br />\n空氣質素唔算差 最緊要係樓下有好多寵物店 我自己有養貓 買嘢比主子們都方便啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9736d88eb7befc2fa782a9a10b28abaf7fdc8e1","tid":2486164,"uid":3179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:35:22.000Z","msg":"太平道同勝利道叫靜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535523bfa8d6e3931bdde560b8c1b171d137fb8d","tid":2486164,"uid":56758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:09:43.000Z","msg":"其實最怕係火車聲<br />\n因為實在太近<br />\n唔知個隔音屏有無效"},{"pid":"14a99992c44ab5ab59e299d9c430efcfadaf6fd6","tid":2486164,"uid":241447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"535523bfa8d6e3931bdde560b8c1b171d137fb8d","tid":2486164,"uid":56758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:09:43.000Z","msg":"其實最怕係火車聲<br />\n因為實在太近<br />\n唔知個隔音屏有無效"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:13:39.000Z","msg":"上年睇過太平閣低層對隔音屏，出奇地靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6831af977079ca8fac4c9337918afb92f2b370e0","tid":2486164,"uid":215164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14a99992c44ab5ab59e299d9c430efcfadaf6fd6","tid":2486164,"uid":241447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"535523bfa8d6e3931bdde560b8c1b171d137fb8d","tid":2486164,"uid":56758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:09:43.000Z","msg":"其實最怕係火車聲<br />\n因為實在太近<br />\n唔知個隔音屏有無效"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:13:39.000Z","msg":"上年睇過太平閣低層對隔音屏，出奇地靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"reply